rComments: Professor Jennifer Harris is one of the best professors I've had! I took 2 classes with her in the same year and switched my major bc she made me look at religion in a new light. Make sure to take a class with her if you can!

I really enjoyed this class, but found the workload to be very heavy for a half credit course.  A lot of group work (4-5 major projects) which was challenging.  Prof. Harris is very knowledgeable, down to earth and kind.  I would take another class with this professor.
Great speaker, made the course material interesting, interested in various pedagogical  techniques, highly reccomend
